---

## Task 2: CsrfGuard — write failing unit test

**Files:**
- Create: `src/unit-tests/csrf.guard.unit-spec.ts`
- Create: `src/modules/auth/guards/csrf.guard.ts` (stub only in this task)

- [ ] **Step 1: Create a stub guard so the test file can import it**

Create `src/modules/auth/guards/csrf.guard.ts`:

```typescript
